<figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="1250" height="700" src="https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Overhead-Triceps-Stretch-1.jpg" alt="Overhead Triceps Stretch" class="wp-image-6384" srcset="https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Overhead-Triceps-Stretch-1.jpg 1250w, https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Overhead-Triceps-Stretch-1-300x168.jpg 300w, https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Overhead-Triceps-Stretch-1-1024x573.jpg 1024w, https://www.endomondo.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Overhead-Triceps-Stretch-1-768x430.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1250px) 100vw, 1250px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">Overhead Triceps Stretch Guide. <span>Photo: Aliaksandr Makatserchyk</span></figcaption></figure>



