<li>To perform the <a href="https://medlineplus.gov/ency/imagepages/19488.htm" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">overhead triceps stretch,</a><sup>[3]</sup> raise your left arm above your head, and bend your left elbow.&nbsp;</li>



<li>Then, let the arm drop at the center of your <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/upper-back-exercises" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">upper back</a>, and use the other hand to apply pressure to the bent elbow. This will deepen the triceps stretch.&nbsp;</li>



